column6: she applies foundation with a large paddle brush
she applies 3 dots of concealer under her eyes and two above her lips
she blends in the concealer with a kabuki brush
she backs away to see how blended the concealer is
she applies setting powder with a round brush under her eyes in a sweeping motion
she applies eye primer to her eyelids and blends with her fingers by sweeping and tapping
she looks at a mirror off camera and jokes about how she is a different person now with concealer on
she applies a light brown eyeshadow all over her eyelids with a blending brush
she applies a pink taupe color to her eyelids' outer corners with a smaller blending brush
she looks at different makeup products
she shows off the NYX tame and frame product and opens it
she shows off the packaging and product size and compares how small the product is to the packaging (product is 1/3 the size of the packaging)
